The paper also discusses the use of different modelling approaches, such as system dynamics, network theory, cellular automata, and agent-based modelling, which are relevant to sub-categories cs.CY (Computational Geometry and Topology), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
